&lt;Z-Seven Fund Inc> said it expects toearn six dlrs a share in 1987, up from 4.20 dlrs a share in1986.    The company said the 1986 net earnings were up 30 pct from3.22 dlrs in 1985. Net asset value in 1986 rose 35 pct to 16.09dlrs a share from 11.89 a year earlier, adjusted for athree-for-two stock split. Reuter&#3;